  "instructions": [
    "in a bowl, mix together cornstarch and a splash of water to create a slurry",
    "add crumbled feta cheese to the slurry and mix until a dough forms",
    "using a syringe, create small spheres with the feta dough and cook in boiling water for 1-2 minutes, or until they float to the surface",
    "heat about 1/2 inch of vegetable oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat",
    "fry the empanadas until golden brown, about 2-3 minutes per side",
    "in a separate pan, cook the empanada dough over medium heat for 1-2 minutes on each side, until lightly browned",
    "allow the empanadas to cool slightly before serving"
